g) that the frequency band 2 010-2 025 MHz is currently allocated to the MSS on a primary basis in Region 2 only;
h) that in Regions 1 and 3, the frequency band 2 010-2 025 MHz may be used by high-altitude platform stations as base stations to provide International Mobile Telecommunications (IMT), in accordance with No. 5.388A;
