recalling
a) the Plan of Action of the World Summit on the Information Society (Geneva, 2003), on e-environment, calling for the establishment of monitoring systems, using information and communication technologies (ICTs), to forecast and monitor the impact of natural and man-made disasters, particularly in developing countries, least developed countries and small economies;
